videos.description: Mustangs safety Mikial Onu comes underneath and picks off Michigan QB Shea Patterson on the 2 yard line.
videos.headline: SMU safety Onu steals one away from Patterson

videos.description: The Wolverines go for it on 4th down and capitalizes with the Ben Mason TD.
videos.headline: Michigan FB Mason pushes ahead for TD

videos.description: SMU QB Ben Hicks lets one fly for a 50-yard pass to WR James Proche to tie the game 7-7.
videos.headline: Mustangs QB Hicks goes deep for 50-yard TD to Proche

videos.description: Wolverines S Josh Metellus sneaks in and picks off SMU QB Ben Hicks and then takes it to the house.
videos.headline: Michigan S Josh Metellus closes the half with a pick-6

videos.description: Michigan QB Shea Patterson floats one up for WR Donovan Peoples-Jones to rein in for a 7-yard score.
videos.headline: Patterson puts it up and Peoples-Jones brings it in for Michigan TD

videos.description: Mustangs backup QB William Brown rolls right and finds TE Ryan Becker for the TD.
videos.headline: SMU backup QB Brown rolls out for 2-yd TD

videos.description: Michigan QB Shea Patterson lets one fly deep to Donovan Peoples-Jones and connects for his third TD.
videos.headline: Patterson goes deep to Peoples-Jones for a third TD

videos.description: Michigan RB Tru Wilson powers through multiple SMU defenders for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Michigan RB Wilson breaks through for 9-yard TD
